### =========================
### READ OPERATIONS
### =========================

### GET ALL LESSONS
GET http://localhost:3000/lessons

###

### GET BEGINNER LESSONS
GET http://localhost:3000/lessons?level=Beginner

###

### GET INTERMEDIATE LESSONS
GET http://localhost:3000/lessons?level=Intermediate

###

### GET ADVANCED LESSONS
GET http://localhost:3000/lessons?level=Advanced

###

### GET ONE LESSON
GET http://localhost:3000/lessons/1


### =========================
### UPDATE LESSON
### =========================

PUT http://localhost:3000/lessons/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lesson Title",
  "level": "Beginner"
}



### =========================
